<div id="help" class="modal hide fade">
    <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
        <h3>Need help?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Here your roadbook in a text editor, you can do what you want ! <br />
        You can change, delete, move, add contents or even create new pages.</p>

        <h4>Action buttons</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Save:</strong> Save your roadbook on the server. You can know the last save date with a hover on this button.</li>
            <li><strong>Export as PDF:</strong> Create your roadbook in PDF, some options are available : format, margins, and a custom header or footer.</li>
            <li><strong>Download as:</strong> You can view your roadbook in HTML to use the print feature from your browser, download an archive to edit with an external software or download in PDF if you have exported it before.</li>
            <li><strong>Delete:</strong> When you click this button your roadbook will be destroyed. There is no undo for this function.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
